                        <div class="js-script-content-wrapper top-margin-script markdown-content">
                                                                                        <a href="https://github.com/knpuniversity/drupal-under-the-hood/edit/master/knpu/create-service.md" target="_blank" class="btn btn-default btn-circle pull-right js-tooltip" title="Edit on GitHub"><span class="fa fa-pencil"></span></a>
                                                                    <p>In <code>RoarController</code>, we use the <code>$count</code> variable to construct either a little
<code>roar</code> or a big <code>rooooooar</code>, depending on what's in the URL:</p>
<p><div class="code-block-wrapper" data-code-block-guid="05a1868311">
