<h2 id="using-a-service-the-long-way">Using a Service (the long way) <a class="headerlink" href="create-service#using-a-service-the-long-way" title="Permalink to this headline"><i class="fa fa-link" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></h2>
<p>Great! Now our imaginary, complex code lives somewhere else. How do we use it? It's
simple!</p>
